{"title":"火光曲","authors":["天马"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":12,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"火光曲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天马"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"报纸消息：美国驻南越芹苴省的新闻处的所有反动书籍和报刊，最近被一批愤怒的少年学生放火烧毁。他们高呼“打倒美帝国主义”等口号。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊熊的火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"烧呀烧得欢；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"熊熊的火焰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红呀红满天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南越的少年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正直又勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺起胸膛来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争在前线。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"强把南越占，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"土地被蹂躏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民受摧残！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可恨美国佬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘴甜心似剑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"吃人血和肉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要把人骗。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国新闻处，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——毒气传播站；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"美国的书刊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——害人的鸦片！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点起一把火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"统统都烧完；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“滚开美国佬！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"口号声震天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人小志不小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正气冲霄汉；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爱国不后人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重担挑在肩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赞歌唱一曲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌颂好少年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争定胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光在前面！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}